It was a happy day! We finally met with Anna in a photo studio, and I did not regret spending a lot of films, she danced, and I took pictures. Our communication with Anna inspires us for the second time. I wish there were more moments like this.
In the evening, Misha and I rented a car for the first time through carsharing and drove around the area. I can't buy my own car yet and I don't have much driving experience, so the determination to even drive around the area gave me a lot of adrenaline and joy.
